            "title": "網球｜鄭欽文罕有掟蕉發洩 幸沉住氣挫梅頓絲 入查爾斯頓網賽8強",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"鄭欽文入查爾斯頓網賽8強。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4112b7b5286046aa2b547be97907f80c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250404/_2025040413372183868.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">鄭欽文入查爾斯頓網賽8強。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周四查爾斯頓網賽女單16強，國家好手鄭欽文遇上梅頓絲。激戰至決勝盤時，鄭欽文疑不滿自己表現，罕有掟蕉發洩，幸她最終沉住氣以盤數2:1取勝，首入此賽事8強，並將自己泥地不敗走勢延至13場。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭欽文吃蕉。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/570a15771f0f73db08c1539430eb6e0e/2025-04/1_0_3.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭欽文吃蕉。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭欽文掟蕉。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6082d40f87147b7db44c9e4dc71459ac/2025-04/2_0_3.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭欽文掟蕉。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭欽文入查爾斯頓網賽8強。WTA官方微博照片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e2bc6f982f82106fc8f944b6c46d7a87/2025-04/543ace57ly1i04ni61zwgj25v93wx4qt.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭欽文入查爾斯頓網賽8強。WTA官方微博照片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭欽文入查爾斯頓網賽8強。WTA官方微博照片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/27ba1d1ea5dee485f35d53ce38dc7238/2025-04/543ace57ly1i03a297azdj22h21nekeh.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭欽文入查爾斯頓網賽8強。WTA官方微博照片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭欽文入查爾斯頓網賽8強。WTA官方X照片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f5db0f1e1ce5e9520028ad97350307d6/2025-04/GnpCnv1WcAAX6fm.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭欽文入查爾斯頓網賽8強。WTA官方X照片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭欽文入查爾斯頓網賽8強。WTA官方X照片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8a570768ca0fa46c30b7e290f1b09618/2025-04/Gnp71vaWoAALkU7.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭欽文入查爾斯頓網賽8強。WTA官方X照片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>鄭欽文罕有掟蕉發洩</h2>\n<p>今場面對世界排名第28位的梅頓絲，鄭欽文首盤打得輕鬆，兩度破發下以6:3先贏一盤。不過，梅頓絲之後上力於第2盤以局數6:3追平盤數。鄭欽文於決勝盤開局表現不濟，第1局即破發。局間休息時，鄭欽文在場邊吃香蕉補充能量，可能因不滿意自己表現，她突然大力將蕉頭掟落地。她發洩後雖於第2局未能破發，但之後沉住氣回勇連處5局，終以6:3贏下決勝盤，以盤數2:1晉級。\n\n</p><h2>「告訴自己要更有侵略性」</h2>\n<p>鄭欽文取勝後鈹得泥地13連勝，且首入此賽事8強，她賽後表示：「決勝盤，我一開始就落後0:2，之後我告訴自己必須打得更有侵略性。天氣很濕熱，從一開始保持專注力真的很難，今場是意志力的考驗，很高興可以取勝，感謝來支持我的觀眾。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062097/即時-體育-網球-鄭欽文罕有掟蕉發洩-幸沉住氣挫梅頓絲-入查爾斯頓網賽8強",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-04 14:11:44",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "珍惜生命｜上水彩玉樓男子墮樓亡",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"彩園邨彩玉樓發生墮樓慘劇。林思明攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/620a45aec1a5473507b8725db03e0f9c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250404/_2025040413593355209.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">彩園邨彩玉樓發生墮樓慘劇。林思明攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今(4日)天中午12時左右，彩園邨一名男子昏伏彩玉樓大廈平台位置，消防到場證實事主已氣絕身亡，毋須送院，懷疑他從高處墮下，警員正調查男子身份及墮樓原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176695/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"彩園邨彩玉樓發生墮樓慘劇。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/711b8389a6c4224e4523222f6d2dedb9/2025-04/02_5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        彩園邨彩玉樓發生墮樓慘劇。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176696/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"彩園邨彩玉樓發生墮樓慘劇。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/081b8efc0e5c65c3dd0a98f0653e9df5/2025-04/03_3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        彩園邨彩玉樓發生墮樓慘劇。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>自殺求助熱線：</strong>\n</p>\n<p>「情緒通」精神健康支援熱線：18111 \n\n</p>\n<p>香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222\n\n</p>\n<p>生命熱線： 2382 0000\n\n</p>\n<p>明愛向晴軒： 18288\n\n</p>\n<p>社會福利署： 2343 2255\n\n</p>\n<p>撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000\n\n</p>\n<p>東華三院芷若園： 18281\n\n</p>\n<p>醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350\n\n</p>\n<p>賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open 噏」：http://www.openup.hk\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
